## Description
Part of https://github.com/apache/incubator-pinot/issues/6904

Add a command to infer the Pinot schema from the JSON data, with the complex type handling.

For example, a run of 
```
JsonToPinotSchema -dateTimeColumnName hoursSinceEpoch -jsonFile  //tmp/test/test.json -pinotSchemaName json-schema -outputDir /tmp/test -unnestFields=payload.commits 
```

